imdb.plot outline: Galaxy Superstar is a talent audition show discovering Indonesian talents who are totally into K-pop and dream of becoming a star like K-pop idol groups. The selected finalists of the survival-type audition show travel to Korea to undergo rigorous training system that has produced wildly popular Korean pop stars. The 6 finalists of 3 months of training in Korea were formed into a girl group, S.O.S (abbreviation of Sensation of Stage).
imdb.title: Galaxy Superstar
plot: A search for talented Indonesians with dreams of becoming future stars of I-Pop (Indonesian popular music), sending them to Korea to go through the K-Pop star training system.::SFC

_Galaxy Superstar_ (qv) is a talent audition show discovering Indonesian talents who are totally into K-pop and dream of becoming a star like K-pop idol groups. The selected finalists of the survival-type audition show travel to Korea to undergo rigorous training system that has produced wildly popular Korean pop stars. The 6 finalists of 3 months of training in Korea were formed into a girl group, S.O.S (abbreviation of Sensation of Stage).::SFC
